Package camzup.kotlin

Class KtVec3

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Vec3
camzup.kotlin.KtVec3
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Vec3>, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Float>
public class KtVec3
extends Vec3
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Float>
Provides Kotlin operator overloading support for three dimensional vectors.
